item.description:
Hi Everyone! I can not believe it is almost Nov!! Our meetup is going to be Nov 5 at 6:30. This months presenter is going to be yours truly Chef KO Bisson. I will be doing a couple of raw food demos. If you have any dishes you would like to see made...let me know. I am up for the challenge :).
As usual it will be a potluck so please bring an organic raw food dish enough for 6-8 people. If you are new and not sure what to bring a salad, fruit or veggie, is always good. Can't wait to see everyone!!
$2 for Adults....Children always free!
If you would like me to make your dish...I would be happy to for $15.

group.name: Manchester Raw Vegan Food Meetup Group

item.name: Nov!! Can you Believe it! Meetup!
